metadata.name: BRUCE: The Dragon Opus
metadata.description: TURBOGRAPH 002:  A detailed visual study of Bruce Lee (李小龍) and his body of work. Incorporating his entire filmography of starring roles from his breakthrough “The Big Boss” to the posthumously released “Game of Death”.  The piece also incorporates Bruce Lee’s role as Kato in “The Green Hornet” as well as his entire published works from 1963-1978.  A homage and celebration of Bruce Lee’s contribution to the culture as a martial artist, teacher, philosopher, and actor. |||| By Shan Vincent de Paul (SVDP) . Contributors: Oussama Hesham, Carlos D Fuentes, Cánido Estudio, Music by La+ch
